# News Watch Daemon — real (non-synthetic) fixtures captured from live APIs.
# The committed *_synthetic.* fixtures are structurally identical and what
# CI runs against. Real captures stay local for occasional offline
# parser-verification work.
daemons/news_watch_daemon/tests/fixtures/finnhub_real_*.json
daemons/news_watch_daemon/tests/fixtures/telegram_real_*.json
# Defensive generic — catches any future daemon's _real.* convention.
**/tests/fixtures/*_real.*
